# Mereta

Mereta is an **unincorporated community** situated in eastern [Tom Green County](/Tom_Green_County,_Texas) within the [U.S._state](/U.S._state) of [Texas](/Texas), United States.  The settlement lies along local roads east of the city of [San Angelo](/San_Angelo,_Texas), which serves as the [county seat](/County_seat) of [Tom Green County](/Tom_Green_County,_Texas).  Mereta is recorded in the [List_of_counties_in_Texas](/List_of_counties_in_Texas) and is identified by the [Geographic_Names_Information_System](/Geographic_Names_Information_System) feature ID 1362628.

